  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 11</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 22 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 10 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 24</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, E</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>An extremely powerful technique devised by the fourth Hokage, this complex technique has you spin Chakra into the palm of your hand, forming a sphere of great power. Once created, the sphere can be used to make a melee touch attack, either as an attack action or as part of a Full Attack. Once used it is discharged regardless of whether it hit. The rasengan can be held for up to 1 round per level before it dissipates.<br><br>A target hit by the rasengan takes 7d8 force damage, and will be pushed back a number of feet equal to half the damage dealt (rounded to the nearest 5 ft unit).</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to increase the damage by 1d8, up to 1d8 per level or 18d8 total, whichever is lower. For every 2 Chakra spent this way, the Perform Requirements of this technique increase by 1.</p>\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
